？）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">tldr : 今晚2000-2130只係一個 和平理性 進行既集會，請大家抽兩個鐘到場，<br />\n因為呢個會係我地暫時可見既 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唯一</span> 出路。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n！！！今晚 626 愛丁堡 8PM 不見不散 ！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"收工即刻嚟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b543d7711d7ea28e72dbe77ebc29558218534b2c","tid":1258230,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c8bc7f684a09ced1aaa71c3b6ba8fc3024ce6043","tid":1258230,"uid":264915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"推返上熱門"},{"pid":"1ca4bfbd4d3598f68fd15680f226faa30a10879e","tid":1258230,"uid":11410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:26:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7173e7baf1944a49c379cdb1197c72faff82e142","tid":1258230,"uid":55005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d28ad829566729b00308fd82f69fe6cffd13b75","tid":1258230,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ff3e9e0b130ae4e802bbf2b5a14fe3b495e398","tid":1258230,"uid":55005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432f550ffce473ff944d4bf734ff189f9068267f","tid":1258230,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:44:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cffb448f904058725fdeaee6f909f923cbee3620","tid":1258230,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:03:12.000Z","msg":"PUS